column1: # This is the ReadMe section for the Pen & Printers Analysis Folder
1. The product_sales.csv file contains the dataset used for the analysis.
2. The PDF file of Pen & Printers New Product Sales Strategy Report details the findings of the analysis.
3. The pen_andprinters.ipynb file contains the Python code that produces the report.
4. The Analysis Instructions PDF file contains the analysis instructions and details about the product_sales.csv dataset.
